      <div type="book">
        <linkGrp type="notes"/>
        <div n="Y20-315P" type="poem"><head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-headnote-1"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1">occasioned by the Death of the Duke of Orleans Regent of France 172</l></lg></head><head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-headnote-2"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1">by D<hi rend="sup">r</hi> 08. Arbuthnot</l></lg></head><head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-headnote-3"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1">Respicite Exemplar Vitæ.</l></lg></head>
      <lg n="1" type="stanza"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-1"> “How Vain are Mortall Man's Endeavours!&#13;</l><l n="2" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-2"> “Said at S<hi rend="sup">t</hi><hi rend="black-letter">James</hi>'s, Master Travers</l><l n="3" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-3"> “Good <hi rend="black-letter">Orleans Dead</hi>!──In truth, 'tis hard!</l><l n="4" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-4"> “May <hi rend="black-letter">States-men</hi> all dye so prepar'd!</l><l n="5" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-5"> “I do foresee (and for foreseeing</l><l n="6" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-6"> He equalls any Man in being)</l><l n="7" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-7"> “The Army ne'er can be disbanded──</l><l n="8" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-8"> “I wish the King were Safely Landed:────</l><l n="9" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-9"> “Ah friends! Great Changes threat this Land;</l><l n="10" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-10"> “All <hi rend="black-letter">France</hi> and <hi rend="black-letter">England</hi> at a Stand!</l><l n="11" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-11"> “There's <hi rend="black-letter">Miriweys</hi> d'ye mark! Strange Work!</l><l n="12" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-12"> “And there's the <hi rend="black-letter">Czar</hi>, &amp; there's the <hi rend="black-letter">Turk</hi>!</l><l n="13" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-13"> “The <hi rend="black-letter">Pope──────An India Merchant</hi> by</l><l n="14" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-14"> Cut short his Speech with this Reply.</l><l n="15" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-15"> “<hi rend="underline">All at</hi> a <hi rend="black-letter">Stand</hi>! <hi rend="underline">You see <hi rend="black-letter">Great Changes</hi></hi>!</l><l n="16" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-16"> “Sir, Did You ever see the <hi rend="black-letter">Ganges</hi>?</l><l n="17" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-17"> “<hi rend="black-letter">There dwells a Race</hi>, we call 'em <hi rend="black-letter">Monkeys</hi>, as our <hi rend="black-letter">Quid nuncis</hi>.)</l><l n="18" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-18"> (Grave, Sober, Sage</l><l n="19" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-19"> “On either Bank, from bough to bough,</l><l n="20" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-20"> “They meet &amp; Chat as we do now,</l><l n="21" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-21"> “Whispers go round, they grin, they Shrug,</l><l n="22" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-22"> “They bow, they Snarle, they Scratch, they hug,</l><l n="23" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-23"> “And just as <hi rend="black-letter">Chance</hi>, or <hi rend="black-letter">Whim</hi> provoke 'em,</l><l n="24" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-24"> “They either Bite their friends, or Stroake 'em.</l></lg><lg n="2" type="stanza"><l n="25" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-25">“There have I seen Some Active Prig,&#13;</l><l n="26" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-26"> “To Shew his Parts, bestride a twig;</l><l n="27" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-27"> “Lord! How the chatt'ring tribe admire</l><l n="28" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-28"> “Not that he's Wiser, but is Higher!</l><l n="29" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-29"> “All long to try the <hi rend="black-letter">Vent'rous thing</hi>,</l><l n="30" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-30"> (For <hi rend="black-letter">Power</hi> is but to have one's <hi rend="black-letter">Swing</hi>)</l><l n="31" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-31"> “From Side to Side he springs, he Spurns,</l><l n="32" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-32"> “And bangs his Foes &amp; Friends by turns,</l><l n="33" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-33"> “Thus as in giddy freaks he bounces,</l><l n="34" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-34"> “Crack goes the twig, and in he flounces,</l><l n="35" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-35"> “Down y<hi rend="sup">e</hi> Swift Stream the <hi rend="black-letter">Wretch</hi> is born</l><l n="36" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-36"> “Never ah! never to return.</l></lg><lg n="3" type="stanza"><l n="37" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-37">“<hi rend="black-letter">Zounds</hi>! what a Fall has Our <hi rend="black-letter">Dear Brother</hi>!</l><l n="38" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-38"> “<hi rend="black-letter">Morbleu</hi>, cries one, &amp; <hi rend="black-letter">Dam──e</hi> 'tother.</l><l n="39" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-39"> “The <hi rend="black-letter">Nations</hi> give a <hi rend="black-letter">Gen'rall Scriech</hi>,</l><l n="40" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-40"> “None cocks his Tail, none claws his br────ch.</l><l n="41" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-41"> “Each trembles for the Publick Weal,</l><l n="42" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-42"> “And for a while forgets to Steal:</l><l n="43" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-43"> “A while all Eyes intent &amp; Steady</l><l n="44" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-44"> “Pursue Him whirling down the Eddy;</l><l n="45" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-45"> “But out of Mind when out of View</l><l n="46" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-46"> “Some other mounts the twig anew,</l><l n="47" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-47"> “And Bus'ness on Each <hi rend="black-letter">Monkey</hi> Shore</l><l n="48" xml:id="spp-Y20-315P-line-48"> “Runs the same track it went before.Y20-315P   </l></lg></div>
